<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Mi Ruta SJR</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.1/font/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito:wght@400;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/image/favicon.ico">

  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --amarillo: #F5C800;
      --amarillo-claro: #FFF8CC;
      --amarillo-dark: #D4A800;
      --sea: #20948B;
      --sea-claro: #E6F5F4;
      --lagoon: #6AB187;
      --burnt: #DE7A22;
      --fondo: #F5F4EF;
      --blanco: #ffffff;
      --texto: #111111;
      --suave: #777;
      --borde: #E8E4D8;
    }

    html, body {
      height: 100%;
      font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
      background: var(--fondo);
      color: var(--texto);
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    /* ── NAVBAR ── */
    .navbar {
      background: var(--blanco) !important;
      border-bottom: 1.5px solid var(--borde);
      box-shadow: none !important;
    }
    .navbar-brand img { height: 36px; }
    .nav-link { font-size: 0.88rem; color: #555 !important; font-weight: 600; }
    .nav-link:hover { color: var(--texto) !important; }

    /* ── PRIMERA PANTALLA ── */
    .first-screen {
      height: calc(100vh - 62px);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    /* ── HERO — mitad superior ── */
    .hero {
      background: var(--amarillo);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      flex: 1;                  /* ocupa exactamente la mitad */
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 0 24px 30px;
    }

    .hero::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0,0,0,0.08) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 28px 28px;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .hero-wave {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -1px; left: 0; right: 0;
      line-height: 0;
    }
    .hero-wave svg { display: block; width: 100%; height: 30px; }

    .hero-inner {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      animation: heroFadeUp 0.6s ease both;
    }

    @keyframes heroFadeUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
      to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    .hero-tag {
      display: inline-block;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
      color: var(--texto);
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 5px 16px;
      border-radius: 100px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(28px, 5vw, 52px);
      font-weight: 900;
      color: var(--texto);
      line-height: 1.05;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .hero p {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
      max-width: 380px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    /* ── ACCESOS — mitad inferior ── */
    .accesos {
      flex: 1;                  /* ocupa exactamente la otra mitad */
      padding: 20px 20px 16px;
      max-width: 860px;
      width: 100%;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .sec-eyebrow {
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--suave);
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .sec-title {
      font-size: clamp(20px, 3vw, 30px);
      font-weight: 900;
      color: var(--texto);
      margin-bottom: 4px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .sec-title span { color: var(--sea); }

    .ac-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-top: 14px;
    }

    .ac-card {
      background: var(--blanco);
      border: 1.5px solid var(--borde);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 20px 20px 16px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--texto);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: transform 0.22s ease, border-color 0.22s, box-shadow 0.22s;
      animation: cardUp 0.5s ease both;
    }

    .ac-card:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
    .ac-card:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.28s; }

    @keyframes cardUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(16px); }
      to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    .ac-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-4px);
      border-color: var(--amarillo);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 28px rgba(245,200,0,0.16);
      color: var(--texto);
    }

    .ac-bg-icon {
      position: absolute;
      right: 10px;
      bottom: -10px;
      font-size: 72px;
      opacity: 0.07;
      line-height: 1;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .ac-icon-wrap {
      width: 42px;
      height: 42px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .ac-icon-yellow { background: var(--amarillo-claro); color: var(--burnt); }
    .ac-icon-teal   { background: var(--sea-claro);     color: var(--sea); }

    .ac-arrow {
      position: absolute;
      top: 16px;
      right: 16px;
      width: 28px;
      height: 28px;
      background: var(--fondo);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--suave);
      transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
    }

    .ac-card:hover .ac-arrow {
      background: var(--amarillo);
      color: var(--texto);
      transform: translate(3px, -3px);
    }

    .ac-card h3 { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 3px; }
    .ac-card p  { font-size: 12px; color: var(--suave); font-weight: 600; }

    .help-line {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 10px 0 0;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--suave);
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .help-line a { color: var(--sea); font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; }
    .help-line a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

    /* ── RESTO (se ve al hacer scroll) ── */
    .stats-section {
      background: var(--texto);
      padding: 56px 20px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .stats-section::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 24px 24px;
    }
    .stats-inner {
      max-width: 860px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 20px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    .stat-item { text-align: center; }
    .stat-num { font-size: 48px; font-weight: 900; color: var(--amarillo); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .stat-label { font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); font-weight: 600; }

    .como {
      padding: 60px 20px 52px;
      max-width: 860px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .sec-eyebrow-dark { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--suave); margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .como-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 20px; margin-top: 36px; }
    .como-item { background: var(--blanco); border: 1.5px solid var(--borde); border-radius: 16px; padding: 24px 18px; }
    .como-num { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--amarillo-dark); letter-spacing: 0.08em; margin-bottom: 12px; display: inline-block; background: var(--amarillo-claro); padding: 3px 12px; border-radius: 100px; }
    .como-icon { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; width: 48px; height: 48px; background: var(--amarillo-claro); border-radius: 12px; margin: 0 auto 10px; color: var(--amarillo-dark); }
    .como-item h4 { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 5px; }
    .como-item p { font-size: 12px; color: var(--suave); font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.6; }

    .vendedor-banner {
      background: var(--amarillo);
      margin: 0 auto 48px;
      max-width: 820px;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }
    .vb-inner {
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 32px 28px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 20px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: var(--amarillo);
    }
    .vb-inner::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0,0,0,0.06) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 20px 20px;
    }
    .vb-text { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
    .vb-text h3 { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 3px; }
    .vb-text p  { font-size: 13px; color: rgba(0,0,0,0.6); font-weight: 600; }
    .vb-btn { position: relative; z-index: 1; background: var(--texto); color: #fff; text-decoration: none; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 800; padding: 11px 22px; border-radius: 10px; white-space: nowrap; transition: opacity 0.18s; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .vb-btn:hover { opacity: 0.82; color: #fff; }

    footer { background: var(--blanco); border-top: 1.5px solid var(--borde); padding: 24px 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 13px; color: var(--suave); font-weight: 600; }
    footer strong { color: var(--texto); }
    footer a { color: var(--suave); text-decoration: none; }
    footer a:hover { color: var(--sea); }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .ac-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .stats-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 24px; }
      .como-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .vb-inner { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }
      .first-screen { height: auto; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- NAVBAR -->
  <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light bg-light shadow-sm">
    <div class="container">
      <a class="navbar-brand me-2" href="#">
        <img src="/image/logo_sin_fondo.png" alt="Logo" style="margin-top:-1px;">
      </a>
      <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarContent">
        <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
      </button>
      <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarContent">
        <ul class="navbar-nav me-auto mb-2 mb-lg-0">
          <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/">Inicio</a></li>
          <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/contacto">Contacto</a></li>
          <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#">Sobre Nosotros</a></li>
          <% if (user && (user.role === "admin" || (user.role && user.role.rol === "admin"))) { %>
            <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/showUser"><i class="fa-solid fa-users-gear"></i> Usuarios</a></li>
            <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/admin"><i class="fa-solid fa-chart-line"></i> Dashboard</a></li>
            <li class="nav-item"> <a class="nav-link" href="/login-vendedor"><i class="fa-solid fa-tag fa-store"></i> Vender</a></li>
            <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/registro_vendedor"><i class="fa-solid fa-tag"></i> Registro para vender</a></li>
          <% } %>
          <% if (user && (user.role === "vendedor" || (user.role && user.role.rol === "vendedor"))) { %>
            <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/panel"><i class="fa-solid fa-store"></i> Mi Panel</a></li>
          <% } %>
          <% if (!user || user.role === "user" || user.role === "normal" || (user.role && user.role.rol === "user")) { %>
            <li class="nav-item"> <a class="nav-link" href="/login-vendedor"><i class="fa-solid fa-tag fa-store"></i> Vender</a></li>
            <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/registro_vendedor"><i class="fa-solid fa-tag"></i> Registro para vender</a></li>
          <% } %>
        </ul>
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-2">
          <% if (user) { %>
            <span class="me-2">Hola, <strong><%= user.username %></strong></span>
            <div class="dropdown ms-2">
              <button class="btn btn-light border rounded-circle" type="button" data-bs-toggle="dropdown">
                <i class="bi bi-list" style="font-size:22px;"></i>
              </button>
              <ul class="dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-end shadow">
                <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="/perfil"><i class="bi bi-person"></i> Ver perfil</a></li>
                <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="/configuracion"><i class="bi bi-gear"></i> Configuración</a></li>
                <li><hr class="dropdown-divider"></li>
                <li><button class="dropdown-item text-danger" id="logout-btn"><i class="bi bi-box-arrow-right"></i> Cerrar sesión</button></li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          <% } else { %>
            <a class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm" href="/register">Registrarse</a>
            <a class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" href="/login">Iniciar Sesión</a>
          <% } %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- ── PRIMERA PANTALLA COMPLETA ── -->
  <div class="first-screen">

    <!-- HERO AMARILLO -->
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-inner">
        <span class="hero-tag">Bienvenido a la plataforma</span>
        <h1>Explora<br>tu ciudad</h1>
        <p>Consulta rutas de transporte y negocios locales disponibles</p>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-wave">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 1440 30" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" preserveAspectRatio="none">
          <path d="M0,15 C360,30 1080,0 1440,15 L1440,30 L0,30 Z" fill="#F5F4EF"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ACCESOS — llenan el resto de la pantalla -->
    <section class="accesos">
      <p class="sec-eyebrow">Accede rápido</p>
      <h2 class="sec-title">Todo lo que<br><span>necesitas</span></h2>

      <div class="ac-grid">
        <a href="/locales" class="ac-card">
          <div class="ac-bg-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-store"></i></div>
          <div class="ac-arrow"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i></div>
          <div class="ac-icon-wrap ac-icon-yellow">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-store"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Comercios</h3>
          <p>Explora y descubre negocios locales</p>
        </a>

        <a href="/rutas" class="ac-card">
          <div class="ac-bg-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot"></i></div>
          <div class="ac-arrow"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i></div>
          <div class="ac-icon-wrap ac-icon-teal">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Rutas</h3>
          <p>Consulta las rutas disponibles</p>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="help-line">
        ¿Necesitas ayuda? <a href="/contacto">Contáctanos</a>
      </div>
    </section>

  </div>
  <!-- FIN PRIMERA PANTALLA -->

  <!-- ── RESTO (se ve al hacer scroll) ── -->

  <!-- STATS -->
  <section class="stats-section">
    <div class="stats-inner">
      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-num">8+</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Rutas de transporte</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-num" style="font-size:28px;padding-top:10px;">San Juan del Río</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Querétaro, México</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-num">100%</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Información local</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CÓMO FUNCIONA -->
  <section class="como">
    <p class="sec-eyebrow-dark">Cómo funciona</p>
    <h2 class="sec-title">Tres pasos <span>simples</span></h2>
    <div class="como-grid">
      <div class="como-item">
        <span class="como-num">01</span>
        <div class="como-icon">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><path d="m21 21-4.35-4.35"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4>Explora comercios</h4>
        <p>Navega por todos los locales y negocios registrados en la plataforma.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="como-item">
        <span class="como-num">02</span>
        <div class="como-icon">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="1" y="3" width="15" height="13" rx="2"/><path d="M16 8h4l3 3v5h-7V8z"/><circle cx="5.5" cy="18.5" r="2.5"/><circle cx="18.5" cy="18.5" r="2.5"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4>Consulta rutas</h4>
        <p>Encuentra la ruta más conveniente para llegar a tu destino.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="como-item">
        <span class="como-num">03</span>
        <div class="como-icon">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 21s-8-7-8-13a8 8 0 0 1 16 0c0 6-8 13-8 13z"/><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="3"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4>Llega fácil</h4>
        <p>Usa el mapa para planear tu trayecto sin complicaciones.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- BANNER VENDEDOR -->
  <% if (!user || user.role === "user" || user.role === "normal") { %>
  <div class="vendedor-banner">
    <div class="vb-inner">
      <div class="vb-text">
        <h3>¿Tienes un negocio local?</h3>
        <p>Registra tu comercio y llega a más clientes en San Juan del Río</p>
      </div>
      <a href="/registro_vendedor" class="vb-btn">Quiero vender →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <% } %>

  <!-- FOOTER -->
  <footer>
    <strong>Mi Ruta SJR</strong>
    <p style="margin-top:6px;">Información de rutas y comercios en San Juan del Río, Querétaro.</p>
    <div style="display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:20px;margin-top:10px;">
      <a href="#">Términos</a>
      <a href="#">Privacidad</a>
      <a href="/contacto">Contacto</a>
    </div>
    <p style="margin-top:8px;font-size:12px;">© 2025 Mi Ruta SJR — Todos los derechos reservados.</p>
  </footer>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  <script>
    const logoutBtn = document.getElementById('logout-btn');
    if (logoutBtn) {
      logoutBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
        fetch('/logout', { method: 'POST' }).then(() => window.location.href = '/login');
      });
    }
  </script>

</body>
</html>
